  "detailed_description": "As a result of an unknown meteorite hitting an unknown planet, a poisonous gas began to spread on the planet. This gas began to mutate animals on the planet.<br><br>Two frogs and a pig that developed as a result of this mutation experienced the first effects of the meteorite impact.<br><br>The pig sees the two frogs and becomes jealous of them, and our adventure begins to unfold. Simple platform game<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623690/extras/5c7fd2bf4cce64c7310298cfb3501e82.poster.avif?t=1706376711\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623690/extras/5c7fd2bf4cce64c7310298cfb3501e82.webm?t=1706376711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623690/extras/5c7fd2bf4cce64c7310298cfb3501e82.mp4?t=1706376711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Prepare to fight in the world of Mutant Frog. Push your flying skills to the limit as you jump across dangerous passages and spiky obstacles.<br>Lots of levels with unique soundtracks!<br>Meticulously designed 16-bit sprites, animations, and backgrounds in the spirit of the classics.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623690/extras/78b670b87218e12dcbfd4bb2037aebcd.poster.avif?t=1706376711\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623690/extras/78b670b87218e12dcbfd4bb2037aebcd.webm?t=1706376711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623690/extras/78b670b87218e12dcbfd4bb2037aebcd.mp4?t=1706376711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>During this mutation process, you may also start using weapons.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623690/extras/16c69beb84ed4c05ed796d4a90684d85.poster.avif?t=1706376711\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623690/extras/16c69beb84ed4c05ed796d4a90684d85.webm?t=1706376711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623690/extras/16c69beb84ed4c05ed796d4a90684d85.mp4?t=1706376711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>-Story mode contains 25+ levels spread over 5+ chapters, levels can be unlocked.<br>-Secret 5 World and 25 Level.<br>-Epic Boss fight",
  "about_the_game": "As a result of an unknown meteorite hitting an unknown planet, a poisonous gas began to spread on the planet. This gas began to mutate animals on the planet.<br><br>Two frogs and a pig that developed as a result of this mutation experienced the first effects of the meteorite impact.<br><br>The pig sees the two frogs and becomes jealous of them, and our adventure begins to unfold. Simple platform game<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623690/extras/5c7fd2bf4cce64c7310298cfb3501e82.poster.avif?t=1706376711\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623690/extras/5c7fd2bf4cce64c7310298cfb3501e82.webm?t=1706376711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623690/extras/5c7fd2bf4cce64c7310298cfb3501e82.mp4?t=1706376711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Prepare to fight in the world of Mutant Frog. Push your flying skills to the limit as you jump across dangerous passages and spiky obstacles.<br>Lots of levels with unique soundtracks!<br>Meticulously designed 16-bit sprites, animations, and backgrounds in the spirit of the classics.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623690/extras/78b670b87218e12dcbfd4bb2037aebcd.poster.avif?t=1706376711\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623690/extras/78b670b87218e12dcbfd4bb2037aebcd.webm?t=1706376711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623690/extras/78b670b87218e12dcbfd4bb2037aebcd.mp4?t=1706376711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>During this mutation process, you may also start using weapons.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623690/extras/16c69beb84ed4c05ed796d4a90684d85.poster.avif?t=1706376711\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623690/extras/16c69beb84ed4c05ed796d4a90684d85.webm?t=1706376711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623690/extras/16c69beb84ed4c05ed796d4a90684d85.mp4?t=1706376711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>-Story mode contains 25+ levels spread over 5+ chapters, levels can be unlocked.<br>-Secret 5 World and 25 Level.<br>-Epic Boss fight",
